{"tid":1642855,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"細路仔先做選擇題","createTime":"2019-10-10T01:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T01:35:31.000Z","uid":176279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"355c78d9610942b3ff7858b18628fece549cfd1a","tid":1642855,"uid":176279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:30:45.000Z","msg":"我地而家舉咗台灣旗就會畀人話港獨（雖然唔舉都會）<br />\n但<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其實why not both</span></span><br />\n1）台灣人支持我地唔係因為搞獨立，而係大家（全世界）都認同自由民主；何況人地都係自稱中華民國<br />\n2）青天白日滿地紅旗一定要有：呢樣嘢可以嚴重挑戰中共嘅統治合法性；特朗普之前都提過唔係唔用啊嘛<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">結論：兩樣都要用<br />\n比例係8:2 <br />\n（大部人用青天白日，少數人帶台灣旗；或者大家自備多啲民國旗，再準備一兩支仔嘅台灣旗）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人，_____</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4c0640bb491fddb401a1769f5e61c01fad47ae24","tid":1642855,"uid":176279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:31:46.000Z","msg":"反抗啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac969df54e5fab1413e7b54e59b3301aad021172","tid":1642855,"uid":100016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"你topic句野都好撚蝗蟲味，咪撚將蝗國野改做廣東話就扮本土啦"}]}